    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-5">
      The Architecture of College Funding: How Technology Is Reshaping Educational Grants
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 italic mb-6">
      From FAFSA modernization to AI-powered scholarship matching, the infrastructure of financial aid is undergoing its most significant transformation in decades. Here's what's actually changing—and what it means for students and families.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-500 mb-10">By TruSchools Staff</p>
  </header>

